io.gearpump.streaming.appmaster

Class DagManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.gearpump.streaming.appmaster.DagManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.Stash, akka.actor.StashSupport, akka.actor.UnrestrictedStash, akka.dispatch.RequiresMessageQueue<akka.dispatch.DequeBasedMessageQueueSemantics>

    public class DagManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.Stash
    Handles dag modification and other stuff related with DAG

    DagManager maintains multiple version of DAGs. For each version, the DAG is immutable. For operations like modifying a processor, it will create a new version of DAG.
